      <title>UMB Financial 正在洽谈收购竞争对手 Bank Heartland</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/umb-financial-in-talks-to-acquire-rival-bank-heartland</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，UMB Financial Corp. 正在洽谈收购竞争对手 Heartland Financial USA Inc.，这将是今年美国最大的区域银行合并案。]]></description>
